OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FITV News reporter Bob Cruwys reports...
OL,8,FA care provider in Torbay says the
OL,9,Fhike in National Insurance in last
OL,10,Fweek's budget could have a devastating
OL,11,Fimpact on the sector.
OL,13,FBay Care says its overall costs will
OL,14,Frise by around 10.5% as a result of
OL,15,Fthe living wage and National Insurance
OL,16,Fincreases.
