OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FKaren Hall who runs the company which
OL,7,Femploys 320 staff and looks after
OL,8,Fhundreds of clients in Torbay and
OL,9,FDevon fears the result could be cuts
OL,10,Fto essential services and jobs,
OL,11,Fforcing more people to go to hospital.
OL,13,FKaren said: "If we are scaling back it
OL,14,Fis counterproductive because all the
OL,15,Fpeople that we are not seeing to will
OL,16,Fbe turning up to hospital so it makes
OL,17,Fno sense to me why this change is
OL,18,Fbeing enforced onto the care sector.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
