OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,F"Actually this is going to cause
OL,7,Fcompanies to close down, make cuts,
OL,8,Fso, again, counterproductive to what
OL,9,Fthey are trying to achieve and I don't
OL,10,Fthink the consultation with real life
OL,11,Fscenarios and employers has taken
OL,12,Fplace and it needs to be revisited."
OL,14,F"I feel like it will set us miles
OL,15,Fback. We have worked for years and
OL,16,Fyears and years to get into the
OL,17,Fposition we are now and it is already
OL,18,Fa fragile sector and all that hard
OL,19,Fwork will be undone and it will make
OL,20,Fthe system unsustainable."
