OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FOne of Bay Care's clients is David
OL,7,FStark whose carer comes in to help get
OL,8,Fhim washed and dressed in the morning.
OL,10,FDavid has dementia and while his wife
OL,11,FChristine was initially reluctant to
OL,12,Fbring carers in two years ago, she now
OL,13,Fsays she wouldn't be able to manage on
OL,14,Fher own.
