OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FChristine said: "It's just been
OL,7,Fmarvellous. I couldn't cope without it
OL,8,Fand I know that if I need help, extra
OL,9,Fhelp during the day, Bay Care are at
OL,10,Fthe end of the phone and I can ring
OL,11,Fthem any time, day or night, and they
OL,12,Fwill come out and help me.
OL,14,F"They bring a breath of fresh air in
OL,15,Fwhen they come in. Just that half an
OL,16,Fhour in the morning, it just takes
OL,17,Fthat pressure off you."
