OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FKaren from Bay Care is now starting a
OL,7,Fpetition asking that all health and
OL,8,Fsocial care providers are exempt from
OL,9,Fthe national insurance rise, in line
OL,10,Fwith the NHS.
OL,12,FIf not, she says, there will have to
OL,13,Fbe more funding from central
OL,14,Fgovernment for local councils so they
OL,15,Fcan support essential care.
OL,17,FThe Government says it's still
OL,18,F'working through' how the change is
OL,19,Fgoing to affect healthcare providers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
