OL,3,CForcing care sector to 'scale back'
OL,4,Cwill put pressure on NHS, says provider
OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "The employer
OL,7,FNational Insurance rise doesn't kick
OL,8,Fin until April, and we will set out
OL,9,Ffurther details on allocation of
OL,10,Ffunding for next year in due course."
OL,12,FIf the Government doesn't address this
OL,13,Ffunding gap, care providers say, the
OL,14,Fimpact on the sector will be
OL,15,Fdevastating.
